h1 Lindt chocolate cafés
section#brief
  h2 The brief: retain and attract customers to Lindt cafés
  .text-flow-columns
    p Lindt chocolates have a strong brand presence in Australia, but Lindt cafés do not. How can Lindt's chocolate cafés become a more attractive destination within Australia's booming café culture?
    p Lindt have a number of cafés in major cities across the globe, serving hot drinks, desserts and meals, as well as selling chocolates.
    p Mix 3 UXers, 2 weeks and a lot of chocolate and here's what you get.

section#research
  h2 The cafés: Lindt cafés have an image problem
  .text-flow-columns
    p Visiting cafés and competitors, observing and surveying customers and staff revealed that the café experience was fantastic, but it had a very traditional image and low awareness, hence a narrow target market.

