section#personas
  h2 The office worker, the tourist, the social butterfly
  .text-flow-columns
    p Clientele to Lindt cafés vary with location, with the majority being locals (John, the office worker) or passers by (Michelle, the tourist). The exception is Sarah, who visits with her friends for special occasions.
    p These customers are middle class and conservative in their tastes, appreciating Lindt's heritage and quality.
