section#feedback
  h2 Final design: innovative, yet familiar
  .text-flow-columns
    p Instead of requiring users to download yet another app, I considered the use of a chat bot. This would be more familiar and still allow one touch ordering, loyalty updates, notifications and friend referral, and require fewer interfaces. Payment would be handled by Apple or Google Pay.
